    "Id": "vehiclechassisdef_MAXIM_C3M",
    "Name": "Maxim (C3M)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Maxim Heavy Hover Transport (C3M)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>8/12 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>165 ICE</color></b>\n\nThe Maxim is a hover APC designed to provide cover fire for deploying infantry and to support them in the field. To that end, the Maxim is heavily armored for an APC and is outfitted with a variety of weapons.\n\nThis version trades the ability to carry infantry for a C3 Master Computer. As the C3 Master can function as a TAG system, the turret-mounted TAG is also removed. To provide additional protection, the machine guns and ammunition of the standard Maxim are replaced by armor.",
